    "text": "Procedure\tMSysGroupMembers GroupName Text; Select\t\tDistinct MSysAccounts_1.Name From\t\t(MSysAccounts inner join MSysGroups on MSysAccounts.SID = MSysGroups.GroupSID) \t\t\tinner join MSysAccounts as MSysAccounts_1 on MSysGroups.UserSID = MSysAccounts_1.SID Where\t\tMSysAccounts.name = GroupName and \t\t\tMSysAccounts.FGroup <> 0 and \t\t\tMSysAccounts_1.FGroup = 0;"
